@graph.rdfs:comment: Class of all Quantitative properties in IUDX. The range of Quantitative properties are objects describing the associated values as well as meta-information associated with the values. Typically, the value of quantiative property isa numeric value. However, in some cases, it may be a string that has to be interpreted as a number.
@graph.rdfs:label: QuantitativeProperty
